race.comment: EPIC PROPORTIONS (2) is one from one over this course and distance and will be rock-hard fit for this contest. Only needs some luck navigating from the sticky draw to be playing a major role in the outcome. KING OF NAPLES (7) is knocking on the door of another victory with consecutive runner-up finishes this time in work. Can go one better against this lot. OUR MAGNUS (3) loves this six-furlong journey with three wins and six placings from 14 attempts. Best figures measure up nicely. ANEMACORE (10) resumes here but is yet to miss a quinella spot in three first-up efforts and a strong showing while fresh would not surprise. AMORE VELOCE (12) next best from the low draw.
